						               													<description>Grow Fairy Kingdoms is a Competitive Plant-Growing Game for 3-6&amp;#10;players, ages 6-and-up.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each player starts with a Base on which to grow their plant.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;There are two phases: the Day when each player chooses tiles to grow their plant, and the Night, when each Thorn on your plant is a chance to prune your rivals.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;There are four main types of tiles: Stems which cause the plant to branch, Flowers for victory points, Thorns for night-attacks, and Leaves for shielding against attacks.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Rare tiles include powerful gold Flowers, Thorns, and Leaves, as well as tiles to place on opponent plants: Caterpillars (to eat opponent tiles) and Rot (to prevent growth).&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In the Night phase, Thorns allow players to roll six-sided die to target the ends of rival plants.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game ends when at least one player survives a night with at least 5 victory points.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Game comes with 98 tiles and one 6-sided die. No reading required.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
